<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Little Hearts Therapy Center — compassionate therapy for children ages 2–17.">
  <title><%= title %> | Little Hearts Therapy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <main id="main-content">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero__grid">
          <div class="hero__content">
            <h1 id="hero-heading">Every child deserves to thrive.</h1>
            <p>Compassionate therapy for children ages 2–17. Speech, behavioral, occupational, and play therapy — all under one roof.</p>
            <div class="hero__actions">
              <a href="/appointments/new" class="btn btn-primary" aria-label="Book a free consultation">Book a free consultation</a>
              <a href="/about#team" class="btn btn-outline-teal" aria-label="Meet our therapists">Meet our therapists</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero__image" role="img" aria-label="Child in a calm therapy setting">
            🧒
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Preview -->
    <section class="section section--white" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__header">
          <h2 id="services-heading">How we help</h2>
          <p>Specialized therapy services tailored to your child's unique needs and strengths.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-4">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card__icon card__icon--teal" aria-hidden="true">💬</div>
            <h3>Speech Therapy</h3>
            <p>Building communication skills through engaging, play-based sessions.</p>
            <a href="/services#speech" class="card__link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card__icon card__icon--coral" aria-hidden="true">❤️</div>
            <h3>Behavioral Therapy</h3>
            <p>Positive behavior support rooted in evidence-based ABA principles.</p>
            <a href="/services#behavioral" class="card__link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card__icon card__icon--mint" aria-hidden="true">✋</div>
            <h3>Occupational Therapy</h3>
            <p>Developing fine motor skills, sensory processing, and daily independence.</p>
            <a href="/services#occupational" class="card__link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card__icon card__icon--yellow" aria-hidden="true">🧩</div>
            <h3>Play Therapy</h3>
            <p>Healing through play — where children express, process, and grow.</p>
            <a href="/services#play" class="card__link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__header">
          <h2 id="how-heading">How it works</h2>
          <p>Getting started is simple. We're here to guide you every step of the way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
            <div class="step__icon" aria-hidden="true">📅</div>
            <h3>Book a consultation</h3>
            <p>Schedule a free 30-minute consultation to discuss your child's needs and goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
            <div class="step__icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
            <h3>Meet your therapist</h3>
            <p>We match your child with a specialist who fits their personality and needs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step__number" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
            <div class="step__icon" aria-hidden="true">🌱</div>
            <h3>Watch your child grow</h3>
            <p>Track progress together through regular sessions and parent updates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="section section--white" aria-labelledby="testimonials-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section__header">
          <h2 id="testimonials-heading">What parents say</h2>
          <p>Real stories from families who found hope and progress at Little Hearts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial__stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="testimonial__quote">"Within three months, our son went from barely speaking to full sentences. The therapists here are truly magical with children."</p>
            <div class="testimonial__author">
              <div class="testimonial__avatar" aria-hidden="true">SM</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial__name">Sarah M.</div>
                <div class="testimonial__role">Parent of a 4-year-old</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial__stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="testimonial__quote">"The behavioral therapy program transformed our daily life. Our daughter's meltdowns decreased dramatically, and she learned coping skills we use at home."</p>
            <div class="testimonial__author">
              <div class="testimonial__avatar" aria-hidden="true">JR</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial__name">James R.</div>
                <div class="testimonial__role">Parent of a 7-year-old</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial__stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="testimonial__quote">"From the first visit, we felt welcomed and understood. The team listens to parents and truly partners with families."</p>
            <div class="testimonial__author">
              <div class="testimonial__avatar" aria-hidden="true">LP</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial__name">Lisa P.</div>
                <div class="testimonial__role">Parent of a 10-year-old</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
